text: Mimozotale is a genus of longhorn beetles of the subfamily Lamiinae,Biolib.cz - Mimozotale. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. containing the following species: subgenus Mimozotale * Mimozotale flavolineata Breuning, 1951 * Mimozotale javanica Breuning, 1957 * Mimozotale sikkimensis (Breuning, 1940) * Mimozotale tonkinea Breuning, 1969 subgenus Parazotale * Mimozotale cylindrica Hayashi, 1981 * Mimozotale longipennis (Pic, 1927) * Mimozotale minuta (Pic, 1926) subgenus Trizotale * Mimozotale flavovittata Breuning, 1975 * Mimozotale trivittata (Pic, 1931) ==References== Category:Desmiphorini
